[CHARACTER CREATION]

I've detected a character concept: **A curious scholar seeking forgotten knowledge** set in **a quiet library filled with ancient tomes**.

How would you like to create your character?

**Option 1: [AIGenerated]** - I'll generate a complete character based on your scholar concept

**Option 2: [StandardDND]** - Traditional step-by-step D&D character creation

**Option 3: [CustomClass]** - Design a custom class if the standard options don't fit

```json
{
  "planning_block": {
    "thinking": "User has provided a character concept (curious scholar). Need to offer creation methods.",
    "choices": {
      "ai_generated": {
        "text": "AI Generated",
        "description": "Let me create a complete scholar character based on your concept"
      },
      "standard_dnd": {
        "text": "Standard D&D",
        "description": "Build step-by-step: race, class, abilities, equipment"
      },
      "custom_class": {
        "text": "Custom Class",
        "description": "Design a unique class tailored to your concept"
      }
    }
  }
}
```
